{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Change VAT Threshold to Profit Earned",
        "additional_details": "How are we expected to pay more in VAT than what we make in profit?\r\n \r\nWith the increasing costs of ingredients and staff wages along with high overheads, it can be almost impossible for small businesses in hospitality to survive due to burdensome tax bills. We believe the Government is crippling businesses and causing closures while big chains continue to make millions of pounds!\r\n",
        "background": "Change the threshold for VAT to profit earned rather than turnover. \r\n \r\nMany small businesses (especially hospitality) have high turnovers but minimal profit!\r\n",
